### Get all chats with default pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/chats/all
Accept: application/json

### Get all chats with custom pagination (first page, 5 items)
GET http://localhost:8080/chats/all?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

### Get all chats with custom pagination (second page, 10 items)
GET http://localhost:8080/chats/all?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get chat by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/chats/byId/123456789
Accept: application/json

### Get chat by ID (example 2)
GET http://localhost:8080/chats/byId/987654321
Accept: application/json

### Get chat by ID (not found case)
GET http://localhost:8080/chats/byId/999999999
Accept: application/json